 *   iris-exif-kml --input ./site-data --style clustered --include-context
 *
 * Features Demonstrated:
 *   â€¢ Multi-modal image processing with context understanding
 *   â€¢ GPS coordinate extraction and intelligent clustering
 *   â€¢ Automated KML generation with 3D visualization
 *   â€¢ Professional report creation with embedded analytics
 *   â€¢ Computer use agent coordination for batch processing
